### Qdrant API Testing

### Health check
GET http://localhost:6333/health

### List all collections
GET http://localhost:6333/collections

### Create collection
PUT http://localhost:6333/collections/apolo-docs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vectors": {
    "size": 1536,
    "distance": "Cosine"
  },
  "optimizers_config": {
    "default_segment_number": 2
  }
}

### Get collection info
GET http://localhost:6333/collections/apolo-docs

### Count points in collection
GET http://localhost:6333/collections/apolo-docs/points/count

### Insert sample point
POST http://localhost:6333/collections/apolo-docs/points
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "points": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "vector": [0.1, 0.2, 0.3],
      "payload": {
        "content": "Sample document",
        "source": "test"
      }
    }
  ]
}

### Search points
POST http://localhost:6333/collections/apolo-docs/points/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vector": [0.1, 0.2, 0.3],
  "limit": 5,
  "with_payload": true
}

### Delete collection
DELETE http://localhost:6333/collections/apolo-docs
